Package: spicy
Title: Descriptive Statistics and Data Management Tools
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Amal", "Tawfik", , "amal.tawfik@hesav.ch", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-2422-1555", ROR = "04j47fz63"))
Description: Extracts and summarizes metadata from data frames, including
    variable names, labels, types, and missing values. Computes compact
    descriptive statistics, frequency tables, cross-tabulations, and
    APA-style reporting tables to support efficient data exploration and
    reporting workflows. Includes an interactive and exportable codebook
    generator for documenting variable metadata, as well as clipboard,
    spreadsheet, and document-oriented export helpers. Designed to
    streamline initial data management, descriptive analysis, and reporting
    workflows within 'R'.
